hopobject.body: An accountancy practice sirenlabs slimify Deutsche Bank raised its ratings on the Chinese solar panelmakers to "buy" from "hold", saying demand is growing a lotfaster than expected since China announced in mid 2013incentives for the sector and initiatives to curb pollution."Companies with scale, international brand recognition anddeep-rooted China relationships stand to emerge as long-termwinners," the brokerage said in a note.
